                        "description":  "Create a concentration water wall at a point within 1 mile for up to 6 rounds. The wall can be up to 300 feet long, 300 feet high, and 50 feet thick; at each later caster-turn start it moves 50 feet away with caught creatures, then each turn end lowers the wall by 50 feet and reduces later damage by 1d10. The spell ends when the wall reaches 0-foot height, caught creatures need a Strength (Athletics) check against the spell save DC to swim at all, and creatures leaving the wall fall to the ground.",
